      <title>出口持续疲软，捷克经济增长低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/czech-economy-grows-less-than-expected-as-exports-remain-weak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克第三季度经济增长低于预期，家庭消费持续复苏，但对主要市场（尤其是德国）的出口仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/czech-economy-grows-less-than-expected-as-exports-remain-weak</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃将收购 Northvolt 电池合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/volvo-car-to-take-ownership-of-northvolt-battery-joint-venture</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车公司 (Volvo Car AB) 正在与陷入财务困境的 Northvolt AB 成立合资企业，在瑞典西海岸建造一家工厂，这凸显了电动汽车市场扩大电池生产规模所面临的重大挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/volvo-car-to-take-ownership-of-northvolt-battery-joint-venture</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党将保持“财政审慎”预算：PGIM</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/labour-to-remain-fiscally-prudent-in-uk-budget-pgim-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PGIM 首席欧洲经济学家 Katharine Neiss 讨论了即将到来的英国秋季预算，并表示她预计工党政府将在 Rachel Reeves 的声明中保持“财政审慎”。她还讨论了预算声明对债券市场可能意味着什么。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/labour-to-remain-fiscally-prudent-in-uk-budget-pgim-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车盈利能力降至疫情以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/vw-profitability-shrinks-to-lowest-since-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团的营业利润率降至新冠疫情爆发以来的最低水平，该疫情迫使该汽车制造商停产并关闭展厅。彭博社的 Oliver Crook 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/vw-profitability-shrinks-to-lowest-since-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员期待里夫斯的预算在桁架时代划清界限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-traders-look-to-reeves-budget-to-draw-line-under-truss-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国交易员们希望工党政府能出台近 15 年来首份预算，以让投资者相信英国再次成为他们资金的安全目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/uk-traders-look-to-reeves-budget-to-draw-line-under-truss-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国避免衰退，欧元区多数经济体实现增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/french-economy-gathers-speed-with-boost-from-paris-olympics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区大部分最大经济体在第三季度均实现增长 — — 甚至德国也避免了人们普遍预期将持续的经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/french-economy-gathers-speed-with-boost-from-paris-olympics</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西方投资者涌入黄金市场，黄金需求突破 1000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界黄金协会称，第三季度全球黄金需求增长约 5%，创下同期最高纪录，消费额首次超过 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
